Package org.moddingx.libx.datagen.provider

Class CommonTagsProviderBase

java.lang.Object
org.moddingx.libx.datagen.provider.CommonTagsProviderBase
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.minecraft.data.DataProvider
public abstract class CommonTagsProviderBase extends Object implements net.minecraft.data.DataProvider
A provider for block, item and fluid tags. You can set your tags in setup. With defaultItemTags, defaultBlockTags and defaultFluidTags, you can add default tags that can be retrieved from the element.
